cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper is about distributed reinforcement learning in simulated environments, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The specific task being solved is pointgoal navigation, which involves robots navigating to specific points in an environment, so robotics (cs.RO) is also a likely sub-category. The paper also discusses transfer learning and scene understanding, which are topics in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the use of multiple machines and synchronization involves distributed systems (cs.SY).
